{
  "texts": [
    "This allows the model to consider the entire image when making a prediction rather than just a specific region's features.",
    "A further method for image processing is to use a transformer-based model in which the self-attention mechanism focuses on various image regions when selecting a prediction.",
    "The transformer-based model is trained to understand the relationships between multiple image regions and makes predictions based on this information.",
    "Self-attention in DL for image processing can be categorized into two main modules: channel attention and spatial attention.",
    "Spatial attention networks."
  ]
}